This thesis was written in Eclipse, using the following plug-ins:

CDT: C development
Available from the Callisto/Europa/whatever Discovery Site.

Aptana Studio: Ruby code editor
http://update.aptana.com/update/studio/3.2/

Subclipse: SVN integration
http://subclipse.tigris.org/update_1.2.x

Scheme Way: editing Scheme code
http://schemeway.sourceforge.net/update-site

Texlipse: Latex IDE
http://texlipse.sourceforge.net
